We have{choir}on Tuesdays, after school and we work hard. We went to the Derby Schools Music Festival with the top recorder group. More than 300 children were there. We came second and got a shield. We had a good time.
Every Tuesday, after choir, there is{Gym club.}A good gymnast comes to take it. We always start by warming up with forward and backward rolls and hand- or head-stands. Then we get out the rest of the mats and the box. We do hand- and neck-springs. Sometimes we use the springboard. At the end of term we do tests to earn badges.
Other school clubs are:{art club, {guitars, computers, football, netball} and {rounders. }
